12:28.250 --> 12:29.517
(clears throat)

12:29.519 --> 12:32.854
How about I give you
a different organ?

12:33.989 --> 12:35.656
My penis.

12:39.278 --> 12:41.162
You said it wrong.

12:41.164 --> 12:42.847
I did not say it wrong!

12:44.032 --> 12:46.117
Thank you all so much
for coming.

12:46.119 --> 12:47.468
If you'll
indulge me,

12:47.470 --> 12:49.003
I would like to share a story

12:49.005 --> 12:51.155
about my dearly departed
grandmother.

12:51.157 --> 12:52.340
MARSHALL:
<i>Oh, God.</i>

12:52.342 --> 12:54.342
<i>News flash, Johnny Ascot:</i>

12:54.344 --> 12:56.461
<i>Lots of people</i>
<i>have dead grandmas.</i>

12:56.463 --> 12:57.828
<i>No, Marshall.</i>

12:57.830 --> 12:59.663
<i>Don't be bitter.</i>

12:59.665 --> 13:01.165
<i>You're here for Lily.</i>

13:01.167 --> 13:03.217
<i>Just look at her,</i>
<i>so professional.</i>

13:03.219 --> 13:06.387
<i>She hasn't sat</i>
<i>on a single piece of art.</i>

13:06.389 --> 13:09.557
<i>You're gonna ride this thing</i>
<i>out with dignity for Lily.</i>

13:09.559 --> 13:12.343
<i>Not one more thing</i>
<i>that might embarrass her.</i>

13:12.345 --> 13:15.563
<i>I will simply stand here.</i>

13:15.565 --> 13:19.016
<i>Perfectly invisible.</i>

13:19.018 --> 13:20.451
And so I dedicate this show

13:20.453 --> 13:22.570
to my grandmother's memory.

13:22.572 --> 13:24.522
Now...

13:24.524 --> 13:27.191
please join me in honoring her

13:27.193 --> 13:31.662
with 60 seconds
of absolute silence.

13:36.134 --> 13:38.336
(clattering)

